"author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ata\u2019 reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, we among the prophets, our eyes will sleep yet our hearts do not sleep.\u201d Source: al-T\u0323abaqa\u0304t al-Kubra\u0301 419 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0634\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u062a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u064a\u064f\u0646\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/seeing-muhammad-in-your-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":32000,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Visions: Seeing the Prophet in your dreams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sees me in a dream has truly seen me, for Satan cannot imitate me.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6994, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2266 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32623,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/aisha-asks-true-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":32000,"position":2},"title":"Aisha on Dreams: O Allah, I ask you for good and true dreams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Urwah ibn al-Zubayr reported: Aisha, may Allah have pleased with her, would say when she intended to sleep, \u201cO Allah, I ask you for good and true dreams, not false dreams, beneficial and not harmful.\u201d When she said this, they knew that she would not say anything more until she\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37642,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/01\/17\/dream-interpretation-optimism\/","url_meta":{"origin":32000,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Visions: Encouragement to interpret dreams optimistically","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, a dream will come to pass in the manner it is interpreted. The parable of this is a man who raises his foot until he places it down. Thus, if one of you sees a dream,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15364,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/seek-refuge-bad-dream-nightmare\/","url_meta":{"origin":32000,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dreams: Refuge in Allah from nightmares","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe good dream is from Allah and the bad dream is from Satan. Whoever sees something he dislikes, let him blow to his left side three times and seek refuge from Satan. Verily, it will not harm him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43034,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/13\/prophecy-good-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":32000,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nubuwwa: No prophecy left except good dreams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing remains of prophecy but glad tidings.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat are glad tidings?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGood dreams.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6990 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u0